&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Aug 2010 09:45:13 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/ceo-da-canonical-debatera-servicos-web-durante-a-linuxcon-brasil-2010</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/ceo-da-canonical-debatera-servicos-web-durante-a-linuxcon-brasil-2010</guid></item></channel></rss>